values: ok its been awhile since i last wrote in her and lets just say i am bac b/c i just had the worst night b4 skool ever and i really just want 2 cry and like vent about it! so ne wayz i have this friend named cris and he is a really sweet guy and he is a great friend but recently he keeps tellin me he has a crush on me i just kept laughin it off b/c i was like w/e i mean i thought he was kiddin in all truth until he kept askin me 4 a date and i was like we need 2 talk b4 i decide b/c it is really complicated and then he didn't say ne thin soo i was like r u mad at me and he was like idk its complicated and thats just bein a jerk b/c he out of alot of ppl i am really not in the mood 2 date ne 1 new i mean i am not ready 2 trust ne 1 after wat happened between me and jared i mean i cared sooo much about him and 4 him 2 betray me the way he did makes me feel stupid and insecure about trusting guys right now. i mean chris didn't even give me a chance 2 explain he was just like w/e n stuff and hiss attitude finally mad me lose it and i said fine i changed my mind noo there i uncomplicated it r u happy and like totally am pissed at him right now i mean i still want 2 b his friend b/c he is a great person 2 talk 2 and he really listens n stuff but i was talkin 2 my friend and she told me that no matter wat my friendship is ruined w/ him b/c u can't b friends with guys that like u b/c she said while u think oooh great me and him r friends n everythin underneath they still like u and thats leadin them on b/c they think cuz u want 2 b friendz that they might have a chance and u no i was sure if he did or didn't thats y i said it was complicated n stuff but w/e my friend is right i can't b friendz w/ him cuz no matter how much i don't want 2 lose his friendship or how good my intentions r i will just end up hurtin him and thats not fair 2 him so i have 2 officially let go of chris and it sucks! n this is the shit that happened the night b4 skool n then arguein w/ him made me think of y i was confused (jared) and i like broke down cryin cuz i still have feelins 4 him which makes it even harder to tell jared no everytime he asks me 2 get back 2gether w/ him but i just don't think i could deal w/ bein hurt that bad ever again i mean i was crushed i never really told ne 1 except u kno who but i was hurt n i think that i am just not ready yet 2 give some1 else the chance 2 crush me like that. my friend that i really told how i felt said maybe i should give him anothwer chance if i really care about him that much b/c every1 makes mistakes and if he didn't relly care about me he wouldn't keep callin and showin up at party's unless he really was sorry and still cared but i just don't kno if i can!! ne wayz just writin about this stuff and ventin is makin me sad soo here is my goodbye 4 the day.

(me:lmfao) i thought it was so funny cuz like i have never heard that b4 it was def. an original. ne wayz i am waitin 4 this air man 2 get here cuz 4 sum reason the air in my FL room is like not workin properly or w/e and i can't leave until he gets here which pisses me off b/c i am soooooooooo bored!! i think u kno that though cuz i am writin in my journal thingy! w/e like i am gonna go call ppl cuz like i can't take bein at my comp this long soo c ya!

ok soo i am stuck at my aunts house right now cuz my sis went 2 go look at colleges w/ my parents sooo i am stuck here and bored as hell!! ne wayz i am waitin 4 leo to call me bac cuz he had 2 go answer the fone to his mother so i am just wastin time right now. but then this kid that like doesn't kno me very well told me he had a crush on me yesterday and i was wat???? n he was all like i am serious and all i could say was thanx!!! but we have like nothin in common! he plays in a rock band and wants me 2 go 2 his show but now i don't kno if i want 2 cuz it might be weird considerin the fact that he has a crush on me n i don't like him bac, i mean he isn't a bad guy or ne thin and he is cute but i am just not interested in him like that i mean i have only known him 4 like 4 or 5 weeks n like i thought we were just friendz! n now i don't kno wat 2 say b/c like i don't want 2 hurt his feelins cuz i still want 2 b friendz n all but like i don't kno wat i should say 2 him!! ahh y does this always happen 2 me my best friend who i have known 4 like my whole life asked me out n when i told him that i didn't think about him that way he got all pissed offf and then when my other friend S. asked me out n i said i didn't want 2 ruin our friendship or w/e he got all weird and we don't talk like we used 2 and i am sick of stuff like this happenin to me cuz like my friend james who i have told like every detail of my personnal life 2 says he is in love w/ me and that he knos he isn't good enough 2 deserve some1 like me and it breaks my heart 2 hear him say that cuz he is a great guy n he deserves so much but like i am soo not in the mood 2 have a serious relationship w/ him or ne1 right now considering the horrible break up i just went through i mean i just broke up w/ jared b/c of wat he did!! i mean y does every1 want 2 get w/ me right now n tell me that they have liked me 4eva i mean give me some time ppl i don't want a relationship right now!!ne wayz i guess i started writin this 2 relieve my stress b/c i can't exactly do this whole lettin them down easy right cuz it keeps endin bad!!! so i am just gonna say 1  b4 sayin goodnite ! man that felt good to do!
